history.content:
No and/or it is up to the Info88 instructor whom you can reach out to and ask.

Sometimes faculty change their minds about this stuff (e.g., for a # of years not only did faculty enforce the CS188 pre-req for 189 but it was so important that when there were limited # of seats they were rationed based on the grade students had received in 188; now, faculty are talking about proposing removing 188 as a pre-req altogether.)
Is it possible to take Info88A, connector for data c8 without taking data c8 before or concurrently? Will this prereq be enforced?
history.subject: Info 88 without Data C8?
